  <li><a href="https://twitter.com/gabrielpeyre/status/905882155527675905">The Optimal Transport geometry of 1-D Gaussians is flat in the (mean,std) plane. #DoesNotWorkIn2D ht</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://twitter.com/gabrielpeyre/status/904430148472143873">Motzkin’s polynomial is positive but is not a sum of squares. #LifeIsHarderIn2D https://t.co/4OeCnzQ</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://twitter.com/gabrielpeyre/status/904040289869975552">The Legendre transform of the Wasserstein distance has a nice expression! #ProbablyUseless https://t</a></li>
